# Security Policy

## Reporting Security Issues

**DO NOT** open public issues for security vulnerabilities in this toolkit.

### How to Report

- Open a [GitHub Security Advisory](https://github.com/anousonephyakeo/flutter-security-toolkit/security/advisories/new)
- Or email: [your-email@example.com]

## Responsible Disclosure

This toolkit is for **authorized security testing only**.

### Always ✅
- Get written permission before testing
- Follow responsible disclosure practices
- Respect applicable laws and regulations
- Test only systems you're authorized to test

### Never ❌
- Test without explicit authorization
- Access unauthorized data
- Exploit vulnerabilities maliciously
- Share vulnerabilities publicly before patches

## Legal Notice

**Unauthorized access to computer systems is illegal.**

This toolkit is provided for educational purposes and authorized security assessments only. Users are responsible for complying with all applicable laws and regulations.

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 2.x     | ✅ Active support  |
| 1.x     | ❌ No longer supported |
